	<Language_en_US>
		<!--General phrases -->
		<!--Greeting (first time meeting) -->
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_HIJIRI_FIRSTGREETING_1">
			<Text>Greetings. I am Byakuren Hijiri. Did you wish to learn the teachings of our temple here?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_HIJIRI_FIRSTGREETING_2">
			<Text>I am Byakuren Hijiri. We here at the Myouren Temple welcome you.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_HIJIRI_DEFEATED_1">
			<Text>I pray that the rest of the world does not fall to your foolish warmongering.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_HIJIRI_POLITE_HELLO_1">
			<Text>Welcome back to Myouren Temple.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_HIJIRI_POLITE_HELLO_2">
			<Text>Hello again, and welcome to Myouren Temple!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_HIJIRI_POLITE_HELLO_3">
			<Text>Nice of you to visit. You are always welcome at our temple.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_HIJIRI_NEUTRAL_HELLO_1">
			<Text>How can I help you?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_HIJIRI_NEUTRAL_HELLO_2">
			<Text>Yes?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_HIJIRI_NEUTRAL_HELLO_3">
			<Text>Welcome back, how can I help you today?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_HIJIRI_HOSTILE_HELLO_1">
			<Text>Oh... It's you...</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_HIJIRI_HOSTILE_HELLO_2">
			<Text>Your ways are not welcome in our temple.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_HIJIRI_HOSTILE_HELLO_3">
			<Text>What are you doing here?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_HIJIRI_HOSTILE_AGGRESSIVE_MILITARY_WARNING">
			<Text>It seems we have something to fear. But that is not true.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_HIJIRI_EXPANSION_SERIOUS_WARNING">
			<Text>I've noticed your lands are getting a little too close. Our temple would appreciate it if you kept some distance.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_HIJIRI_REQUEST">
			<Text>I hate to do this, but the Myouren Temple is in need of help.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_HIJIRI_LUXURY_TRADE">
			<Text>It's deeds we need, not words.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_HIJIRI_OPEN_BORDERS_EXCHANGE">
			<Text>I'm glad we could come to this agreement.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_HIJIRI_ATTACKED_BETRAYED">
			<Text>You will gain nothing from this foolish warmongering.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_HIJIRI_ATTACKED_EXCITED">
			<Text>I'm sorry to do this, but you must be stopped.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_HIJIRI_ATTACKED_HOSTILE">
			<Text>Let us fight with beautiful danmaku.</Text>
		</Row>
